1
00:00:58,240 --> 00:00:58,640
Dad.

2
00:01:14,239 --> 00:01:15,040
Jealous, huh?

3
00:01:15,879 --> 00:01:18,959
If you got to choose all over again,

4
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:21,159
with Mom and Dad protecting you

5
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:23,200
and living without a care,

6
00:01:24,439 --> 00:01:26,359
you'd cherish it, right?

7
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:36,719
You'd really give me everything you have?

8
00:01:37,319 --> 00:01:38,920
My illness can't be cured.

9
00:01:39,359 --> 00:01:42,040
It'd be a waste not to give them to you.

10
00:01:48,359 --> 00:01:48,959
Don't worry.

11
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,439
I'll definitely cherish

12
00:01:50,439 --> 00:01:51,760
everything you leave me.

13
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,519
Come on, eat.

14
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:54,840
Aren't you hungry?

15
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,319
Thank you, Jiang Lai.

16
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:30,400
Jiang Lai.

17
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:31,879
I will definitely cherish

18
00:02:31,879 --> 00:02:33,199
the life you gave me.

19
00:02:46,919 --> 00:02:47,599
Wait.

20
00:02:51,479 --> 00:02:52,240
Who are you?

21
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:54,599
I'm...

22
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:55,800
Liu Xia.

23
00:02:57,319 --> 00:02:58,520
So it was you.

24
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,039
Miss Jiang Lai.

25
00:03:27,319 --> 00:03:28,080
Miss Jiang Lai.

26
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,599
Miss Jiang Lai.

27
00:03:30,159 --> 00:03:30,879
Miss Jiang Lai.

28
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:36,319
Sorry, Mr. Sheng told me to eat it.

29
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:41,479
Jiang Lai...

30
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,639
I just brought a fake spoon.

31
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,199
Just to have a meal at your place.

32
00:03:47,719 --> 00:03:48,800
No need to be so mad, right?

33
00:03:56,039 --> 00:03:56,520
Get out.

34
00:03:57,479 --> 00:03:58,280
From now on,

35
00:03:58,719 --> 00:03:59,719
don't let me see you two

36
00:03:59,719 --> 00:04:00,560
anywhere near my home.

37
00:04:03,599 --> 00:04:04,280
I heard

38
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:06,280
when speaking to the cops,

39
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,919
you said nothing good about Liu Dazhuang.

40
00:04:12,639 --> 00:04:13,919
Are you really that heartless?

41
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,639
When Liu Xia was alive,

42
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,800
he didn't give a damn.

43
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,959
Now she's dead, he suddenly feels guilty.

44
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:19,319
He doesn't deserve any sympathy.

45
00:04:20,319 --> 00:04:21,519
Liu Xia was my best friend.

46
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:24,120
I know she wouldn't want me to go soft.

47
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:26,560
I'm not a Bleeding heart like Lin Siqi.

48
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,160
In my book,

49
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:29,199
in life,

50
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,959
it should be An eye for an eye.

51
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,199
But to me,

52
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:36,160
you're trying to kill two birds with one stone.

53
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,600
First, you use Liu Xia's death

54
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:41,519
to incite Liu Dazhuang to go after Lin Siqi.

55
00:04:41,759 --> 00:04:42,560
If it works,

56
00:04:42,879 --> 00:04:44,040
you not only get rid of

57
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,639
the obstacle to marrying into the Sheng family,

58
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,199
you also smoothly remove

59
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:48,560
Liu Dazhuang, that Thorn in the side.

60
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:49,839
After all,

61
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:51,800
he's your real father, after all.

62
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,560
And the only one who might expose you.

63
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:56,240
I don't know what you're talking about.

64
00:04:57,319 --> 00:04:58,800
You've got quite an imagination.

65
00:04:58,800 --> 00:04:59,959
You know exactly what I mean.

66
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:04,480
I don't care about the Liu Xia and Jiang Lai stuff.

67
00:05:04,879 --> 00:05:05,560
But

68
00:05:05,839 --> 00:05:07,560
if you mess with Lin Siqi again,

69
00:05:08,079 --> 00:05:09,399
don't blame me for getting ruthless.

70
00:05:13,959 --> 00:05:15,360
Lin Siqi already

71
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,839
made you such a huge cuckold,

72
00:05:17,279 --> 00:05:18,279
yet you still defend her at every turn.

73
00:05:18,839 --> 00:05:19,680
Didn't expect

74
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,680
you to be such a Sentimental fool.

75
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:25,800
Zhang Xiaobei.

76
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,879
Since you won't take the way out I gave you,

77
00:05:34,079 --> 00:05:35,199
don't blame me for being ruthless.

78
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:37,399
After all, you're not the only one

79
00:05:37,839 --> 00:05:38,879
who can see through secrets.

80
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:42,560
And here's a friendly reminder:

81
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:45,360
you'd better keep some things safe.

82
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:58,639
Where the hell did it go?

83
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,399
And Jiang Lai...

84
00:06:01,079 --> 00:06:02,199
Why did she call me Zhang Xiaobei?

85
00:06:04,079 --> 00:06:04,879
Could it be...

86
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:48,519
You can go now.

87
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,600
Work hard next month.

88
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:51,879
I'll double your pay.

89
00:06:52,439 --> 00:06:53,920
Th-thank you, Young Master.

90
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:02,160
Have a seat.

91
00:07:08,399 --> 00:07:09,560
Being a servant for your family is great.

92
00:07:09,759 --> 00:07:10,720
Getting paid from both sides.

93
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,240
But if your father finds out

94
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,600
you're dealing so gently with

95
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,519
someone who betrayed you,

96
00:07:16,079 --> 00:07:17,519
he'll blow his top again, won't he?

97
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,519
When did you find out

98
00:07:20,199 --> 00:07:21,319
I had the Key of Fate?

99
00:07:22,199 --> 00:07:23,920
I heard Sheng Yuanzhou ran through a storm

100
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,000
just to rush home for dinner,

101
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:26,839
wolfing it down

102
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,079
without caring about his image.

103
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,720
That made me suspicious.

104
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:32,879
Plus, you tried to clear Zhang Xiaoyu's name,

105
00:07:33,439 --> 00:07:35,680
and you overreacted to that text.

106
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,399
That pretty much confirmed it.

107
00:07:38,279 --> 00:07:41,120
So you've been plotting in the Sheng family for a while.

108
00:07:41,319 --> 00:07:42,439
Just basic homework.

109
00:07:42,959 --> 00:07:45,439
After all, I've wanted to marry you for ages.

110
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,639
Taking my Key of Fate

111
00:07:51,959 --> 00:07:52,680
won't do you any good.

112
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:57,079
Because I always planned

113
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,600
that when the time came,

114
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:00,439
I'd return to my original identity.

115
00:08:01,519 --> 00:08:03,160
But if the time hasn't come yet,

116
00:08:03,439 --> 00:08:04,800
and Sheng Yuanzhou...

117
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,240
No.

118
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:10,439
If Sheng Shizhong finds out you're a fake son,

119
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,160
what do you think will happen?

120
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,639
Who'd believe something that crazy?

121
00:08:19,959 --> 00:08:21,120
Seems you don't know much about

122
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,279
the Key of Fate after all.

123
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,839
If you use someone else's Key of Fate,

124
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,160
it restores

125
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:28,000
the memories that person used the Key of Fate

126
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,199
to tamper with.

127
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,959
Which means...

128
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:34,440
I used your Key of Fate to have a meal.

129
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:37,399
Now I remember everything.

130
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:42,799
You're Zhang Xiaobei.

131
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:47,000
What do you want?

132
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,360
But you don't need to be afraid.

133
00:08:49,919 --> 00:08:51,000
I have no intention of exposing you.

134
00:08:51,799 --> 00:08:52,679
Then what do you want?

135
00:08:55,799 --> 00:08:56,480
I want to...

136
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,159
be your wife.

137
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,440
You must be completely insane.

138
00:09:06,159 --> 00:09:07,120
Then let's test it out.

139
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:10,000
And see who ends up crazy in the end.

140
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,159
Miss Jiang Lai isn't home.

141
00:09:35,639 --> 00:09:36,799
It's fine. I'll just wait in her room.

142
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:37,639
No, no.

143
00:09:37,879 --> 00:09:38,799
When Miss Jiang Lai isn't here,

144
00:09:38,799 --> 00:09:40,360
no one is allowed in her room.

145
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:41,679
Even when I clean,

146
00:09:41,679 --> 00:09:42,919
I have to do it when she's out.

147
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:45,240
Why don't you wait for her downstairs?

148
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:47,159
Jiang Lai is so on guard...

149
00:09:47,159 --> 00:09:48,320
She must be hiding something in her room.

150
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:48,879
Fine.

151
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:50,799
Then I'll wait for her in the dining room.

152
00:09:51,679 --> 00:09:52,360
This way, then.

153
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,600
I'll make you a cup of tea.

154
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,000
Okay.

155
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,440
My stomach suddenly hurts a bit.

156
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,759
The restroom is this way. I'll take you.

157
00:10:03,759 --> 00:10:04,840
No need. Isn't it right there?

158
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:05,960
I know where it is. I'll go myself.

159
00:10:06,639 --> 00:10:07,799
While I'm in the bathroom,

160
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:09,120
can you make me a cup of...

161
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:11,000
Lemon, ginger, lavender,

162
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,440
and honey Pu-erh tea?

163
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,039
The lemon has to be juiced.

164
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:15,240
The ginger has to be minced.

165
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,679
Three grams of lavender.

166
00:10:16,679 --> 00:10:18,399
Pu-erh, the second steep after boiling.

167
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:20,000
Only half a teaspoon of honey.

168
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:20,759
Got it?

169
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,120
Got it.

170
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,799
Don't mess up a single detail.

171
00:10:23,799 --> 00:10:24,720
I'll be able to tell.

172
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:25,600
Go on.

173
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:08,399
Didn't think you'd be this impatient.

174
00:12:08,799 --> 00:12:09,720
Is it ready?

175
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:10,639
It's ready.

176
00:12:12,519 --> 00:12:13,840
You're such a pain.

177
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,559
You said you were treating me to dinner,

178
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:16,879
to talk about Lin Siqi,

179
00:12:17,279 --> 00:12:18,279
but after all this time,

180
00:12:18,519 --> 00:12:20,200
you've had me posing and acting for photos.

181
00:12:20,799 --> 00:12:21,639
What are you really up to?

182
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,200
You really can't change

183
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,480
your Young Master temper, can you?

184
00:12:29,919 --> 00:12:31,799
These Chenpi Short Ribs are pretty good.

185
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:34,320
It's just that the chenpi is ten years old.

186
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:36,080
If it were 20 years old,

187
00:12:36,639 --> 00:12:37,399
it'd taste even better.

188
00:12:39,399 --> 00:12:40,960
Well, aren't you suffering.

189
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,679
Zhang Xiaobei...

190
00:12:44,919 --> 00:12:46,279
How could I say something like that?

191
00:12:46,559 --> 00:12:48,080
Such picky taste.

192
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,799
So what about Lin Siqi did you want to tell me?

193
00:13:00,039 --> 00:13:00,600
Nothing.

194
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,240
I just wanted to remind you

195
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:04,360
to treat my best friend right.

196
00:13:04,759 --> 00:13:07,279
She truly loves Zhang Xiaobei.

197
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:24,240
What do you mean?

198
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:25,120
I'm warning you.

199
00:13:25,679 --> 00:13:26,600
If I catch you again

200
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:28,039
doing anything that breaks trust,

201
00:13:28,320 --> 00:13:29,759
it won't be as simple as making Sheng Yuanzhou

202
00:13:29,759 --> 00:13:30,799
pose with a spoon for a staged photo.

203
00:13:30,799 --> 00:13:32,799
After all, I just want to be Sheng Yuanzhou's wife.

204
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:34,600
Whoever Sheng Yuanzhou is,

205
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:35,840
I don't care.

206
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:14,120
Dad.

207
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:15,840
There's nothing to eat at home.

208
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:17,759
Can you give me some money?

209
00:14:24,559 --> 00:14:25,000
Dad!

210
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:25,960
What?

211
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,200
I'm hungry.

212
00:14:27,519 --> 00:14:28,840
Go away. Don't bother me.

213
00:14:33,879 --> 00:14:34,840
Asking for money now?

214
00:14:35,399 --> 00:14:36,080
What money?

215
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:37,480
I have no money to give you.

216
00:14:37,919 --> 00:14:38,960
I can't even feed myself.

217
00:14:51,039 --> 00:14:51,519
What's wrong?

218
00:14:52,399 --> 00:14:53,039
Jealous?

219
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:55,559
Guess you're not that heartless after all.

220
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,240
How did you know I was here?

221
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:04,200
Don't you shop at this mall all the time?

222
00:15:04,799 --> 00:15:06,159
Seems like you've been paying attention to me.

223
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:07,440
What,

224
00:15:07,879 --> 00:15:08,879
you finally interested in me?

225
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:10,279
Not interested.

226
00:15:10,519 --> 00:15:11,879
That's why we need to build some chemistry.

227
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:14,799
What do you mean?

228
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:16,759
Don't you want to be my wife?

229
00:15:17,159 --> 00:15:18,639
Then we have to build some chemistry, right?

230
00:15:20,159 --> 00:15:21,879
You're not after something else, are you?

231
00:15:22,679 --> 00:15:24,360
I heard Liu Dazhuang confessed.

232
00:15:24,879 --> 00:15:25,480
So I came to see you.

233
00:15:25,919 --> 00:15:26,799
To comfort me?

234
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:28,399
Do you need comforting?

235
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:30,639
There's a cafe up ahead.

236
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:32,120
I'll treat you to a drink.

237
00:15:32,559 --> 00:15:32,919
Let's go.

238
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:37,000
Drink it. I lost.

239
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:39,679
I don't drink sugary drinks.

240
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:44,360
I bought it just for you.

241
00:15:44,679 --> 00:15:45,080
Sugar-free.

242
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:47,840
Being rich

243
00:15:48,399 --> 00:15:49,759
isn't that much fun.

244
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:51,919
You just get pickier.

245
00:15:52,480 --> 00:15:53,600
No sugary drinks.

246
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:54,840
No low-quality carbs.

247
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:56,519
Time's measured by the second.

248
00:15:58,080 --> 00:16:00,080
Don't you feel you miss out on simple joys?

249
00:16:24,519 --> 00:16:25,519
Simple joys...

250
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:27,240
I think I'm starting to understand

251
00:16:27,519 --> 00:16:28,960
why Lin Siqi chose you,

252
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:30,120
instead of Sheng Yuanzhou.

253
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:04,200
Seduction doesn't work on me.

254
00:17:05,119 --> 00:17:06,400
Don't forget our deal.
